o's World Map", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_customskinloader", "label": "CustomSkinLoader", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Gives offline-mode / TLauncher players skins too."}, {"id": "changelog_terralith", "label": "Terralith", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_regions_unexplored", "label": "Regions Unexplored", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Substitute for Oh The Biomes You'll Go, which has no 1.20.1 release (team skipped to 1.21)."}, {"id": "changelog_valkyrien_skies", "label": "Valkyrien Skies", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Ships/airships/mechs physics pillar (2.4.11 + Eureka + Clockwork + Trackwork + Immersive Aircraft). Incompatible with OptiFine."}, {"id": "changelog_lycanites_mobs", "label": "Lycanites Mobs", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "1.20.1 official port, alpha but content-complete: 287 creatures, 6 dungeon schematics, DeferredBossSpawner (boss per floor), all 3 raid bosses; verified by inspecting the jar directly rather than trusting metadata."}, {"id": "changelog_ice_and_fire", "label": "Ice and Fire: Community Edition", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_no_tree_punching", "label": "No Tree Punching", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Verified the exact mod RLCraft uses for knapping flint into shards, a flint knife, and cutting grass for plant fiber."}, {"id": "changelog_mo_bends", "label": "Mo' Bends", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Character/mob animations, client-side only. Chosen over player-model mods (MPM/CPM) that hard-conflict with it. The swap to add a character creator is one line: drop Mo' Bends, add More Player Models."}, {"id": "changelog_dynamic_trees", "label": "Dynamic Trees", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Was installed but inert (replaceVanillaSapling=false); shipped config turns it on, plus Dynamic Trees Plus and Dynamic Trees \u2013 Biomes O' Plenty so BOP trees are dynamic too."}, {"id": "changelog_itemphysic", "label": "ItemPhysic Full", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_reskillable_reimagined", "label": "Reskillable Reimagined", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The actual Reskillable lineage on 1.20.1 with skill-gated items/blocks \u2014 the RLCraft mechanic, not an approximation. Replaced PMMO."}, {"id": "changelog_pmmo", "label": "PMMO (replaced)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_apotheosis", "label": "Apotheosis", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_curios", "label": "Curios / Artifacts / Relics", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_origins", "label": "Origins Forge + Classes", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Race/identity system (not levelling), so it sits alongside progression mods. Removed in parity pass then re-added; players pick an origin on first spawn."}, {"id": "changelog_better_combat", "label": "Better Combat", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_tough_as_nails", "label": "Tough As Nails", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Thirst + temperature; tuned-fair analog of RLCraft's Simple Difficulty."}, {"id": "changelog_solo_leveling", "label": "Cromta's Solo Leveling", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "The one deliberate non-RLCraft system (levels, ranks, shadow army, Igris quest). Ships no structure_set entries so it does not disturb the spacing datapack. /gamerule SoloLevelingXPGain paces it against Reskillable."}, {"id": "changelog_solo_leveling_addon", "label": "Cromta's Solo Leveling Addon", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_kleiders_custom_renderer", "label": "Kleider's Custom Renderer API", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Undeclared hard dependency of Solo Leveling that packwiz does not resolve. Replaces player models, so it may conflict with Mo' Bends; untestable from a dedicated server \u2014 verify in game."}, {"id": "changelog_antixray", "label": "AntiXray", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Server-side ore obfuscation \u2014 replaces hidden ore with fake stone in chunk packets; the only thing that defeats xray resource packs. Shipped config sets global default enabled=true (mod default false would leave modded dimensions unprotected)."}, {"id": "changelog_mod_whitelist", "label": "Mod Whitelist", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Anti-cheat Layer 3: kicks clients running blacklisted cheat mods (freecam, fullbright, killaura, baritone, radar/ESP). Shipped strict:false because the mod default strict:true with empty allow-lists would kick every player."}, {"id": "changelog_auth", "label": "Auth mod", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Anti-cheat Layer 2 password login, required because online-mode=false lets anyone connect under any username. Chosen over Simple Login because Auth is server-side only \u2014 players install nothing (matters for TLauncher)."}, {"id": "changelog_simple_login", "label": "Simple Login (rejected)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_battle_towers", "label": "Battle Towers (Modrinth remake)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Replaces BrassAmber BattleTowers, which is excluded from the CurseForge API and would permanently break auto-updates."}, {"id": "changelog_brassamber_battletowers", "label": "BrassAmber BattleTowers (excluded)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "changelog_curseforge_api_excluded", "label": "CurseForge API-excluded mods problem", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Mods excluded from the CurseForge API cannot be fetched programmatically, which would permanently break packwiz auto-updates for every player \u2014 so they cannot be used at all."}, {"id": "changelog_chunky", "label": "Chunky (pre-generation)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}], "edges": [{"source": "changelog_canary_vs_conflict", "target": "changelog_canary", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/CHANGELOG.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "changelog_canary_vs_conflict", "target": "changelog_valkyrien_skies", "relation": "references", "confi